OL,3,CTravel disruption in the Midlands as
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast train managers strike
OL,6,FPassengers are being warned of
OL,7,Fdisruption to services as train
OL,8,Fmanagers at Avanti West Coast strike
OL,9,Fover how much they are paid for
OL,10,Fworking on rest days.
OL,12,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,13,FTransport (RMT) union are walking out
OL,14,Fon New Year's Eve and 2 January.
OL,16,FThe strikes are set to affect every
OL,17,FSunday from 12 January to 25 May.
