OL,3,CTravel disruption in the Midlands as
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast train managers strike
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast strongly advised its
OL,7,Fcustomers to travel either side of the
OL,8,Fstrikes, saying that a "significantly
OL,9,Freduced" timetable will be in place on
OL,10,Fthe two strike days.
OL,12,FThe strikes are set to cause
OL,13,Fdisruption between Birmingham New
OL,14,FStreet and London Euston, with
OL,15,Fremaining trains to the capital from
OL,16,Fother operators likely to be
OL,17,Fparticularly busy as a result.
