OL,3,CTravel disruption in the Midlands as
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast train managers strike
OL,6,FAvanti said it will run one train an
OL,7,Fhour between Euston and Birmingham. On
OL,8,F2 January it will run one train an
OL,9,Fhour between Euston and Wolverhampton.
OL,11,FThe operator said it remains open to
OL,12,Fworking with the union to resolve the
OL,13,Fdispute.
OL,15,FChiltern Railways is putting on
OL,16,Fadditional trains on 2 January between
OL,17,FLondon Marylebone and Birmingham.
