OL,3,CTravel disruption in the Midlands as
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast train managers strike
OL,6,F"On the two strike days we'll have a
OL,7,Fsignificantly reduced service, so
OL,8,Fcustomers with tickets for 31 December
OL,9,For 2 January are strongly advised to
OL,10,Ftravel on alternative dates or claim a
OL,11,Ffull fee-free refund.
OL,13,F"We remain opening to working with the
OL,14,FRMT to resolve the dispute."
