OL,3,CTravel disruption in the Midlands as
OL,4,CAvanti West Coast train managers strike
OL,6,FThe RMT said it rejected Avanti's
OL,7,Flatest offer of #300 or more to
OL,8,Fmanagers to cover working on rest days
OL,9,Fsuch as Sunday.
OL,11,FMick Lynch, RMT general secretary,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Avanti West Coast created this
OL,13,Fdispute by ignoring train managers'
OL,14,Fconcerns and presenting offers those
OL,15,Fmembers deemed unacceptable.
OL,17,F"The company must come forward with a
OL,18,Frevised proposal so we can avoid more
OL,19,Fstrike action further into 2025."
